// TextArea
// Multi-line textarea with label, validation, and optional character count display.

FUNCTION handleChange(e)
  Updates internal value state.
  Calls the onChange callback with the new value.

---

FUNCTION handleBlur(e)
  Runs validation on the current value.
  Sets error message state if validation fails.

---

FUNCTION TextArea(props) -> ReactNode                                     EXPORT
  Renders a labeled textarea.
  IF maxLength is set, shows a character count indicator below the field.
  Shows a validation error message when invalid.
